Game Title: Bomb expert
Game Tags: Minesweeper, Bomb Expert, Sapper

Game Category: Arcade/Puzzle

Game Description:
 Original Minesweeper with 6 themes. Locate all the mines as quickly as possible without uncovering any of them. Plays just like the classic Windows game. Use your mouse to uncover all the squares. Click to reveal a square. A number indicates the total number of mines on the 8 squares around it.


You have to run this game on WAMP server. It
 

